So now you've got
to like, oh no.

00:15:41.840 --> 00:15:43.650
JASON: You can see
yourself performing.

00:15:43.650 --> 00:15:45.830
DAVID: Technology in that way.

00:15:45.830 --> 00:15:47.080
JASON: What's next?

