So yeah, we have begun
working on new songs

00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:13.782
and we'll be jamming
them tomorrow.

00:17:13.782 --> 00:17:14.490
JASON: I love it.

00:17:14.490 --> 00:17:15.270
See what sticks.

00:17:15.270 --> 00:17:15.770
I love it.

00:17:15.770 --> 00:17:16.597
Fantastic.

