This is what I consider
a fun question,

00:17:29.239 --> 00:17:30.280
and it's for each of you.

00:17:30.280 --> 00:17:31.650
So we'll go down the row.

00:17:31.650 --> 00:17:34.680
So a lot of times when
somebody is new to Google,

00:17:34.680 --> 00:17:40.350
