that's who you're listening to,

00:17:54.850 --> 00:17:56.380
who would that be?

00:17:56.380 --> 00:18:01.690
Maybe like Justin
Bieber, Britney Spears,

00:18:01.690 --> 00:18:02.980
something like that.

00:18:02.980 --> 00:18:04.330
Anything that you guys have?

00:18:04.330 --> 00:18:08.140
JOEY: Leo Sayer, "You Make
