You sing along to it?

00:18:11.050 --> 00:18:12.122
Top of the lungs?

00:18:12.122 --> 00:18:13.330
JOEY: It just makes me happy.

00:18:13.330 --> 00:18:13.870
JASON: Yeah?

00:18:13.870 --> 00:18:15.140
I love it.

00:18:15.140 --> 00:18:17.066
Charles, you got on?

00:18:17.066 --> 00:18:19.720
CHARLES: I don't know if I
have a funny one or anything.

00:18:19.720 --> 00:18:21.820
JASON: It doesn't
have to be funny.

00:18:21.820 --> 00:18:23.290
CHARLES: I don't
have a Leo Sayer.

