Lately I've been
listening to this guy.

00:18:35.480 --> 00:18:37.170
Hector Lavoe.

00:18:37.170 --> 00:18:41.060
He's a Puerto
Rican salsa singer.

00:18:41.060 --> 00:18:43.580
He's passed away now, but
he made a lot of records

00:18:43.580 --> 00:18:47.180
