00:18:47.180 --> 00:18:53.450
They'd make these, in the
'60s, early '70s, records.

00:18:53.450 --> 00:18:58.040
But that's what I've
been when I want peppy.

00:18:58.040 --> 00:18:59.250
JASON: I love it.

00:18:59.250 --> 00:19:00.650
David?

00:19:00.650 --> 00:19:02.720
DAVID: Well, it's tough.

00:19:02.720 --> 00:19:06.020
I don't think it's, what do
