00:19:06.020 --> 00:19:09.670
but Steely Dan and Rush.

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:11.540
JASON: Classics.

00:19:11.540 --> 00:19:13.320
Those are inspirations
too, right?

00:19:13.320 --> 00:19:15.040
That's fantastic.

00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:16.610
Paz, what about you?

00:19:16.610 --> 00:19:19.660
PAZ: I guess I
would be embarrassed

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:22.080
