00:19:25.819 --> 00:19:28.360
JASON: Just making noise that
sounds good along to the music.

00:19:28.360 --> 00:19:29.360
PAZ: That sounds French.

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:30.800
Kind of French-like.

00:19:34.020 --> 00:19:35.970
JASON: I was really
hoping that one of you

00:19:35.970 --> 00:19:37.876
would say you listen to
the Pixies in the car

00:19:37.876 --> 00:19:39.000
while you guys are driving.

00:19:39.000 --> 00:19:40.130
PAZ: I definitely
have done that.

00:19:40.130 --> 00:19:41.500
I definitely have done that.

00:19:41.500 --> 00:19:42.930
JASON: Just jamming
out to your own music.

00:19:42.930 --> 00:19:44.730
I would just die if I
pulled up next to one of you

00:19:44.730 --> 00:19:46.229
