00:19:55.850 --> 00:19:58.690
If it drives well,
it sounds good.

00:19:58.690 --> 00:20:00.292
JASON: I love it.

00:20:00.292 --> 00:20:02.250
That's what we listen to
most of our music too.

00:20:02.250 --> 00:20:03.165
Very cool.

00:20:03.165 --> 00:20:07.560
JOEY: I feel like I opened up
my soul with saying Leo Sayer.

00:20:07.560 --> 00:20:08.940
JASON: You led off strong.

